content:
在项目 `D:\code\temp\SpecForge` 中执行 TASK-22。

## 目标
完善 WorkflowDefinitionFile JSON Schema 类型定义。

## 步骤

1. 先读取现有文件：
   - `packages/workflow-runtime/src/types/` 目录下所有文件
   - `packages/workflow-runtime/src/types/workflow-definition.ts`
   - `packages/workflow-runtime/src/types/state-machine.ts`
   - `packages/workflow-runtime/src/types/gate-definition.ts`
   - `packages/workflow-runtime/package.json`

2. 完善 `packages/workflow-runtime/src/types/workflow-definition.ts`：

```typescript
interface WorkflowDefinitionFile {
  id: "feature_spec" | "bugfix_spec" | "feature_spec_design_first" 
    | "quick_change" | "change_request" | "refactor" | "ops_task" | "investigation";
  displayName: string;
  intentKeywords: string[];
  stateMachine: {
    initial: string;
    states: Record<string, {
      agent: string | null;
      skills: string[];
      produces: string | null;
      gate: {
        tool: string;
        composite?: {
          mode: "sequential" | "parallel";
          failPolicy: "fail_fast" | "collect_all";
          children: GateRef[];
        };
      } | null;
      next: { onPass: string; onFail: string; onBlocked?: string };
      retry?: { maxAttempts: number; onExhausted: "blocked" | "debugger" };
    }>;
  };
  artifacts: ArtifactDefinition[];
}

interface ArtifactDefinition {
  name: string;
  path: string;
  required: boolean;
}

interface GateRef {
  gateName: string;
  tool: string;
}
```

3. 确保 `packages/workflow-runtime/src/types/index.ts` 导出所有新类型

4. 验证编译：`npx tsc --noEmit --project packages/workflow-runtime/tsconfig.json`

返回修改了哪些文件和编译结果。
